9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to children; amending 10 O.S. 2021,
Section 404.1, as amended by Section 343, Chapter
11 486, O.S.L. 2025 (10 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 404.1),
which relates to the Oklahoma Child Care Facilities
12 Licensing Act; modifying provision related to
criminal history record searches; and providing an
13 effective date.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 10 O.S. 2021, Section 404.1, as
18 amended by Section 343, Chapter 486, O.S.L. 2025 (10 O.S. Supp.
19 2025, Section 404.1), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 404.1. A. On and after November 1, 2013:
21 1. Prior to the issuance of a permit or license, owners and
22 responsible entities making a request to establish or operate a
23 child care facility shall have:
24
