6 pursuant to paragraph 10 of this subsection,
7 d. a criminal history records and sex offender registry
8 search conducted by an authorized source, when the
9 individual has lived outside this state within the
10 last five (5) years,
11 e. a search of the Department of Corrections' files
12 maintained pursuant to the Sex Offenders Registration
