14 f. a search of any available child abuse and neglect
15 registry within a state the individual has resided in
16 within the last five (5) years,
17 g. search of the nontechnical services worker abuse
18 registry maintained by the State Department of Health
19 pursuant to Section 1-1950.7 of Title 63 of the
20 Oklahoma Statutes, and
21 h. a search of the community services worker registry
22 maintained by the Department of Human Services
23 pursuant to Section 1025.3 of Title 56 of the Oklahoma
24 Statutes;
