13 promulgate rules to identify circumstances when a criminal history
14 records search or foster parent eligibility assessment for an
15 applicant or contractor, or any person over the age of thirteen (13)
16 years residing in a private residence in which a child care facility
17 is located, shall be expanded beyond the records search conducted by
18 the Oklahoma State Bureau of Investigation or as otherwise provided
